<br>      
<p> - You will play <strong>20</strong> rounds of this simulation. In each round, you will be randomly rematched with 3 other donors and 2 other creators, so in every round you are playing with a different set of people. You will not know who else you are playing with.</p>    

<p> - In each round, the credits you earn will be added to a running total. At the end of the experiment, your credits will be exchanged for cash at a rate of (<strong><%= CREDITS_TO_DOLLAR_RATE %> credits for $1</strong>).</p>